INTERNET SOFTWARE AND SERVICES

THE COMPANY IS FOCUSED

ON DELIVERING SEAMLESS INTEGRATION WITH AND ACCESS TO THE INTERNET THROUGHOUT THE COMPANYS PRODUCTS AND SERVICES. THE COMPANYS INTERNET SOLUTIONS ADHERE TO MANY INDUSTRY STANDARDS TO PROVIDE AN OPTIMIZED USER EXPERIENCE. SAFARI 5

